2007: Institute for Quality Management, Inc.[12]
2007: The Wexford Group International[13]
2007: Athena Innovative Solutions, Inc.[14]
2007: Areté Software Ltd (CACI Ltd.) [15]
2007: Dragon Development Corporation[16]
2008: SoftSmart Ltd (CACI Ltd.)[15]
2009: EzGov Europe (CACI Ltd.)[17]
2009: Monitor Media (CACI Ltd.)[18]
2010: SystemWare, Inc.[19]
2010: TechniGraphics, Inc.[20]
2010: Applied Systems Research, Inc.[20]
2011: Pangia Technologies, LLC[21]
2011: Paradigm Holdings, Inc.[22]
2011: Advanced Programs Group, LLC[23]
2012: Delta Solutions and Technologies, Inc.
2012: Tomorrow Communications.[24]
2012: Emergint Technologies, Inc.[25]
2013: IDL Solutions, Inc.[26]
2013: Six3 Systems, Inc.[27]
2016: L-3 National Security Solutions, Inc. (L-3 NSS), PENDING REGULATORY APPROVAL [28]
2016: Purple Secure Systems (CACI Ltd.) [29]


